<D>__{no one does. that's why therapists can charge so much.}
<A>__{as she gathers her belongings, leopold spots a very high heeled red shoe in kate's bag.}
<C>__{leopold}
<D>__{what exactly transpires during therapy?}
<C>__{kate}
<D>__{leopold. a gentleman does not ask those questions. come on, we'll get you home.}
<C>__{leopold}
<D>__{i am perfectly able to travel homeward myself.}
